These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-1::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, mouse, pony, rat
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, daffodil, orchid, lily
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person who growslily is somewhere between the person who growsballoon-flower and the owner of the mouse##7
 3. the owner of the dog and the person who growslily have the same parity positions##9
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
 5. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
 7. the person who growslily is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who growsorchid##6
 9. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |   4    |      5       |
| Pet     | hedgehog | pony     | dog        | mouse  | rat          |
| Sport   | balloon-flower  | begonia | lily | daffodil | orchid |

