.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-2::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, banana, carrot, orange, zucchini
5 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, monopoly, go, canasta
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person playing go##7
 3. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 4. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person playing go##7
 5. the person eating asparagus is the person playing whist##1
 6. the person eating banana is in the middle##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 8. the person eating asparagus and the person playing mah-jongg have different parity positions##9
 9. the person eating asparagus and the person playing monopoly have different parity positions##9
10. the person playing whist is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
11. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the person eating orange##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Food    | carrot  | asparagus | banana  | zucchini | orange     |
| Hobby   | canasta | whist   | monopoly | go  | mah-jongg |

