.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice, milk
There 5 different types of food: kale, onion, pumpkin, pear, raspberry
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
 2. the person eating kale and the person drinking milk have different parity positions##9
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person eating kale##6
 4. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 5. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 6. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating raspberry have different parity positions##9
10. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person eating raspberry and the person drinking juice##7
11. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
12. the person eating pear is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |       5        |
| Beverage   | milk     | juice     | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | fanta          |
| Job        | pumpkin | kale | onion | pear         | raspberry |

