.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-4::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, house, r&b, reggae, disco
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goldfish, rat, snake
 1. the fan house is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
 2. the owner of the snake is not to the left of the fan house##8
 3. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the fan house##5
 4. the fan disco is somewhere between the fan reggae and the owner of the goldfish##7
 5. the owner of the bird and the fan r&b have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the fan disco##8
 7. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 8. the fan indie is not to the left of the fan r&b##8
 9. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
10. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the fan reggae##8
11. the fan indie is not to the left of the owner of the bird##8
12. the fan house is in the middle##1
13. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
14. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage   | r&b    | indie  | house | disco        | reggae |
| Pet        | goldfish | bird | snake    | chinchilla | rat      |

