 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
 9. the person watching western movies is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
10. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
11. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |    3     |      4      |   5   |
