 7. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
 8. the person who's sport is badminton and the person watching fantasy movies have the same parity positions##9
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's sport is handball is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching horror movies##2
12. the person watching horror movies and the person who's sport is handball have different parity positions##9

