 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the swisher-smoker##8
 9. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the montecristo-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2     |      3      |      4      |      5      |
